message.body: Hi! Are you free and in NY tonight by any chance?! Came back to see my bfs family and if you're free I'd love to swing by your place and say hi before we head back but no pressure!
Hey!! I won't be home until like 6, and I'm super hungover, but I'd love to say hi! And you can see my new paintings
Yayayayay well we are with his little sisters so I thought maybe when they went to bed? So 8? Is that too late? Later is good too but earlier might be tricky
No, later is better so I can chill out after work
But not too late cause I am fried haha. I'm at 31 olive street, keep me posted
1/2 Heeey... So I finally got home, and I think I was being a little ambitious about how I'd be feeling. I think I just need to crash. But you'll pass throug
Can't wait to see your paintings :)
